  #if ((defined(__APPLE__) || defined(__OSX__)) && (defined(__GNUC__) && (__GNUC__ > 2 || (__GNUC__ == 2 && (__GNUC_MINOR__ > 95)))))
      #undef likely
      #undef unlikely
      #define likely(x)   __builtin_expect(!!(x), 1)
      #define unlikely(x) __builtin_expect(!!(x), 0)
  #endif
